{"tid":2423720,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"董建華籲每人都應接種","createTime":"2021-02-26T05:39:14.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-26T09:34:18.000Z","uid":230530,"like":2,"dislike":17,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"f20789149732c1a6ba5e98a444b62b746413cf67","tid":2423720,"uid":230530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-26T05:39:14.000Z","msg":"董建華：團結可以戰勝病毒<br />\n<br />\n全國政協副主席、前行政長官董建華早上到銅鑼灣中央圖書館的疫苗接種中心，接種科興疫苗。他接種後表示，感覺非常好，「一啲都無事」，呼籲每人都應接種疫苗，保護自己、家人及香港，相信團結可以戰勝病毒。<br />\n<br />\n多名前高官亦到中央圖書館接種疫苗，前衛生署長林秉恩期望，市民不要浪費機會、前食物及衛生局長高永文提醒市民接種後，仍要記得戴口罩，以及洗手防疫。"},{"pid":"639f2013358b1ee41ff27908ea3a0fc73228c06d","tid":2423720,"uid":2772,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-26T05:40:38.000Z","msg":"一d都冇事<br />\n似足支那賤種扮香港人講嘢"},{"pid":"3c19632ccd8bf910345635d62f4bb118b2ba0c5f","tid":2423720,"uid":32511,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-26T05:42:22.000Z","msg":"黑氣石又黎料<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8674ed8062b219e360cfd85e8bdccb19672cabe7","tid":2423720,"uid":355748,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-26T05:42:45.000Z","msg":"啱呀聽我懵伯伯講快啲打針<br />\n打完好似魔鬼隊咁勁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d209adde9dcbee0f6955c9f6c0ed359933c52ef5","tid":2423720,"uid":33868,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-26T05:43:08.000Z","msg":"打完仲有無腳痛"},{"pid":"a2b4a5d3e99cf3be3e9d91fdb6ae05581d7d602b","tid":2423720,"uid":14350,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-26T05:45:01.000Z","msg":"分分鐘過一排瓜埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"88ab3dd3030cc77e15801f3f382e1e647e408762","tid":2423720,"uid":11291,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"reply